   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Leon, presbyter, to the presbyters and deacons who share the local service, beloved brothers in the Lord God, fullness of joy.  Our brother Ammonius, who is coming to you, receive in peace; through him we and those with us greet you and those who are with you kindly in the Lord.  I pray for your health in the Lord God.  Emmanuel is my witness. Amen.</ab>
         </div>
